<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Papelería El Bunker</title>
  <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
  <style>
    .animated-bg {
      background-size: 400% 400%;
      animation: gradientMove 15s ease infinite;
    }
    @keyframes gradientMove {
      0%{background-position:0% 50%}
      50%{background-position:100% 50%}
      100%{background-position:0% 50%}
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body class="min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center bg-gray-900">
  <div class="absolute inset-0 animated-bg bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-700 via-pink-500 to-orange-400 opacity-80"></div>
  <div class="relative z-10 w-full max-w-4xl px-6">
    <div class="text-center">
      <div class="flex justify-center mb-6">
  <img src="../Assets/Logopapeleria.jpg"
       alt="Logo Papelería El Bunker"
       class="w-64 h-64 object-cover rounded-full shadow-2xl ring-4 ring-white/30 hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-500">
</div>
      <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-extrabold text-white drop-shadow-lg">
        Papelería <span class="text-yellow-300">El Bunker</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-4 text-lg md:text-xl text-white/90 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Todo lo que necesitas en un solo lugar. Material escolar, de oficina y más.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-10 bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-xl rounded-3xl shadow-xl p-8 inline-block">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white mb-4">Bienvenido</h2>
        <p class="text-white/80 mb-6">Acceda a su cuenta para gestionar las ventas e inventario de la papelería</p>
        <a href="/login" class="inline-block px-8 py-3 bg-yellow-400 text-gray-900 font-bold rounded-full shadow hover:bg-yellow-300 hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-300">
          Iniciar Sesión
        </a>
      </div>
      <p class="mt-8 text-sm text-white/60">
        © 2025 Papelería El Bunker – Todos los derechos reservados
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
